main event: A witness reported seeing a bright oblong UFO that changed colors while fishing in Fremont, Wisconsin on 2 July 1952.
interesting points: The UFO appeared to hover motionless before accelerating rapidly,The sighting was related to a previous incident reported on 6-21-52,The witness estimated the object's movements to be unlike any conventional aircraft,The sighting lasted for approximately 5-10 minutes,There was no photograph included in the report.
witness description: The witness was fishing with companions at the time and had a background in technology and medical research.
